  • The data tables have shared ids:

FMX: Family number
HHX: Household number
FPX: Person number
RECTYPE: Table id

SEX: gender
MRACRPI2: Race coded to single/multiple race group
HISPAN_I: Race/ethnicity recode  >>have more categories than HISCODI3
HISCODI3
1 Hispanic; 2 Non-Hispanic White; 3 Non-Hispanic Black; 4 Non-Hispanic Asian; 5 Non-Hispanic All other race groups.
